---
title: Our thoughts about web development, startups and entrepreneurship
pageable: false
---

- blog.articles.each do |article|
  %article.preview
    %h2
      = link_to article.title, article

    %em Posted on
    %strong= article.date.strftime('%b %e, %Y')
    %em by
    %strong= article.data['dc:creator']
    - if article.tags.any?
      %em in
      %ul.tag-list
        - article.tags.each do |tag|
          %li
            = link_to tag, tag_path(tag)

